article_title: CBO Has No Idea What The Repeal Of The Affordable Care Act Means For The Economy

article_metadata.author: Business in the Beltway

og.description: This is what the Congressional Budget office really said about the budgetary and economic effects of repealing the Affordable Care Act: It has no idea.
